The '''2001-02 season of the [[Liga I Feminin|Divizia A Feminin]]''' was the 12th season of [[Romania]]'s premier women's [[football (soccer)|football]] league. Two divisions (West/South) with 3/4 teams each played a sextuple round robin. First two places in each division qualified to the final tournament (single-leg semifinals and finals).

