==Club career== <!---------------------------------- ===Vushtrria=== {{Empty section|date=February 2018}} ===Trepça'89=== {{Empty section|date=February 2018}} -----------------------------------> ===Diósgyőri=== On 25 January 2018. Hasani joined [[Nemzeti Bajnokság I]] side [[Diósgyőri VTK|Diósgyőri]], on a free transfer.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.almakos.com/zyrtare-florent-hasani-kalon-nga-trepca-89-te-diosgyori-ne-hungari|title=Zyrtare: Florent Hasani kalon nga Trepça’89 te Diosgyori në Hungari|trans-title=Official: Florent Hasani passes from Trepça’89 to Diosgyori in Hungary|website=Almakos|language=Albanian|date=25 January 2018|accessdate=25 January 2018}}</ref> Four days later, the club confirmed that Hasani's transfer was permanent.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dvtk.eu/14833-Florent_Hasani_a_DVTK_jatekosa-cikk-labdarugas|title=Florent Hasani a DVTK játékosa|trans-title=Florent Hasani is a DVTK player|publisher=[[Diósgyőri VTK]]|language=Hungarian|date=29 January 2018|accessdate=29 January 2018}}</ref> On 20 February 2018, he made his debut in the [[2017–18 Magyar Kupa#Fourth round proper|2017–18 Magyar Kupa]] fourth round versus [[Dunakanyar-Vác FC|Vác]], playing full-90 minutes in a 2–0 away win.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://futbollikosovar.com/florent-hasani-debuton-te-skuadra-e-re-ne-eliten-e-futbollit-hungareze/|title=Florent Hasani debuton te skuadra e re në eliten e futbollit hungarezë|trans-title=Florent Hasani debutes at the new team in the top flight of Hungarian football|website=Futbolli Kosovar|language=Albanian|date=21 February 2018|accessdate=21 February 2018}}</ref>
==International career== ===Under-21=== On 21 March 2017. Hasani received a call-up from [[Kosovo national under-21 football team|Kosovo U21]] for a [[2019 UEFA European Under-21 Championship qualification Group 5|2019 UEFA European Under-21 Championship qualification]] match against [[Republic of Ireland national under-21 football team|Republic of Ireland U21]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ffk-kosova.com/federata/?p=17931|title=Lista e futbollistëve të Përfaqësueses U21|trans-title=List of the players of national U21 team|language=Albanian|publisher=[[Football Federation of Kosovo]]|date=21 March 2017}}</ref> and made his debut after being named in the starting line-up.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ffk-kosova.com/federata/?p=18137|title=Kosova U21 e pafat kundër Irlandës, humb me rezultat të ngushtë|trans-title=Kosovo U21 unlucky against Ireland, loses with a close result|publisher=[[Football Federation of Kosovo]]|date=25 March 2017|accessdate=25 March 2017}}</ref>
===Senior=== On 22 January 2018. Hasani received his first call-up from [[Kosovo national football team|national senior team]] in a [[Exhibition game|friendly match]] against [[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.korneri.net/lajmi-i-fundit-lista-e-kosoves-kunder-azerbeixhanit/|title=Lajmi i fundit: Lista e Kosovës kundër Azerbajxhanit|trans-title=Breaking news: List of Kosovo versus Azerbaijan|publisher=Korneri|language=Albanian|date=22 January 2018|accessdate=22 January 2018}}</ref> The match however was cancelled two days later, which prolonged his debut.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.affa.az/index.php/news/friendly-match-cancelled/61160|title=Friendly match cancelled|publisher=[[Association of Football Federations of Azerbaijan]]|date=25 January 2018|accessdate=25 January 2018}}</ref>
