'''Nireas Lamias''' is an [[aquatic sports]] club, founded in 1998, in [[Lamia (city)|Lamia]], [[Greece]]. As of the 2013-2014 season, the club participates in the [[A1 Ethniki Water Polo|A1 Division]] replacing [[NO Chania]], which withdrew from the championship.<ref>{{cite web|title=Νηρέας και επίσημα στην Α1 πόλο|url=http://www.novasports.gr/polo/ellada/article/80760/nireas-kai-episima-stin-a1-polo/|publisher=novasports.gr|accessdate=24 August 2015}}</ref> In the 2014-15 season Nireas Lamias was relegated to A2 Ethniki.<ref>{{cite web|title=Υποβιβάστηκε ο Νηρέας Λαμίας|url=http://www.sport24.gr/Sports/Polo/ypovivasthke-o-nhreas-lamias.3441127.html|publisher=sport24.gr|accessdate=24 August 2015}}</ref>
