The '''Greece women's national handball team''' is the national team of [[Greece]]. It takes part in international team handball competitions. It is controlled by the [[Hellenic Handball Federation]].

The team participated at the [[2004 Summer Olympics]], where they placed 10th.<ref name=sref>{{cite web|title=Greece Handball at the 2004 Athina Summer Games |publisher=Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/GRE/summer/2004/HAN/ |accessdate=18 December 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227072927/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/GRE/summer/2004/HAN/ |archivedate=27 December 2010 |df= }}</ref>

